user.biography:
@elementcase is the original innovator; turning up the volume on iPhone case design since 2007.
We repost #elementcase

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase, and @pelican. May be an image of text that says 'GENUINE PELICAN® CASE'.

node.text: The right case for the job, the BLACK OPS AirPods Case delivers the protection you’ve come to depend on from @elementcase.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase, and @apple. May be an image of phone and wrist watch.

node.text: Make your EDC stand out, and provide the extreme protection your lifestyle demands. The @elementcase collection delivers protection for your @apple AirPods, Apple Watch, and iPhone.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase. May be an image of text that says 'THEELEMENT ELEMENT CASE c LABOR DAY STTEWIDE 20 OFF SALE'.

node.text: Shop and save during the @elementcase Labor Day Sale! September 2nd through the 6th, 2021, take 20% OFF your purchase sitewide (offer only valid in the US).

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: You won't be afraid of heights when your gear is protected by @elementcase. The BLACK OPS Apple AirPods Case will give you the confidence to go anywhere with your listening device.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: Elevate your EDC game—protect your @apple AirPods with the BLACK OPS AirPods Case by @elementcase.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase. May be an image of phone.

node.text: Put it on! and give your iPhone military-grade protection with @elementcase's innovative impact deflection points which diffuse shock away from your device, so your gear is always ready for duty.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: Extreme protection plus tactical style—the BLACK OPS AirPods Case by @elementcase is the perfect way to carry and protect your @apple AirPods and AirPods Pro.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: The impact-dissipation geometry deflects and absorbs shock to deliver superior drop protection that exceeds military spec MIL-STD-810H—the @elementcase SPECIAL OPS for iPhone 12/12 Pro/12 Pro Max/12 Mini is the right case for the job of protecting your device.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: A tactical approach to phone protection—the BLACK OPS X3 by @elementcase delivers MIL-SPEC armored protection, a retractable kickstand for hands-free viewing, a sliding lens cover, and a removable card magazine because rugged and practical are not mutually exclusive.

node.text: Aggressively rugged—the BLACK OPS @apple AirPods Case by @elementcase brings undeniable protection and exceptional style to how you carry and protect your AirPods.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: The newest addition to the BLACK OPS Collection delivers the mil-spec protection you’ve come to expect from @elementcase, and now it features a removable card magazine, protective lens cover, and for tactical cred, an integrated glass breaker because you never know.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase. May be an image of phone.

node.text: Your phone will never fear heights with the SPECIAL OPS by @elementcase, a rugged case that delivers military-grade protection which provides impact deflection points to diffuse shock away from your device, so your gear is always ready for duty.
